resources.string: amalola inu kuti kudzuka ndi chipangizo ndi kawiri pogogoda pa ndi chophimba.

amalola inu kuti kugwirizana USB zipangizo. Liti adamulowetsa ena chipangizo okhudzana USB ntchito, chotero monga ADB ndi MTP, nditero osati kukhala lilipo mpaka izi ndi wolumala kapena ndi chipangizo ndi rebooted. osati onse USB zipangizo nditero ntchito.
Kwambiri ndi tilinazo wa ndi kukhudza yotchinga kotero chikunena mungathe kukhala anawerengedwa pamene atavala magolovesi.
Kumathandiza ndi lachiwiri SIM khadi kagawo. izi ayenera osati kukhala adamulowetsa kupatula Apo ndi ndi SIM khadi mu ndi lachiwiri kagawo. (Amafuna Kuyambiransoko!)

Izi ntchito kuzungulira nkhani ndi Snapchat, Instagram ndi ena kanema kujambula mapulogalamu. ntchito ndi sakani avc encoder mmalo wa ndi hw avc encoder. inu mulole amafunika kuti yambitsaninso ndi app kapena yambitsaninso ndi chipangizo pamaso izi kolowera amatenga kwenikweni. izi mulole komanso chifukwa ena kanema kujambula mapulogalamu osati kuti ntchito.
Thokozani inu onse chifukwa inu kuthandiza!
